	<text>
		<body>
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001928_0001"><!--pb/@n='35r'--></pb>
<lb/><p rend="center"><placeName><settlement type="village">Moembedzi</settlement></placeName> <date when="1863-06-14">14<hi rend="sup">th</hi> June 1863</date></p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My dear <persName>Waller</persName></p>
<lb/><p>As <persName>Wikatani</persName>
<lb/>returns this morning 
<lb/>I send the seven rings 
<lb/>which came from 
<lb/><persName>Clementino</persName> for <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi>
<lb/>Thornton</persName> and 
<lb/>thanks for the 
<lb/><term type="plant">Turnip</term> seed &amp; 
<lb/><bibl>Journal</bibl></p>
<lb/><p>I am very much 
<lb/>ashamed to find 
<lb/>

     

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001928_0002"><!--pb/@n='35v'--></pb>
<lb/>myself guilty of 
<lb/>allowing the numbers 
<lb/>of "<bibl>All the year round</bibl>" 
<lb/>to get out of my 
<lb/>sight. The first 
<lb/>number went first 
<lb/>and gradually all 
<lb/>the rest so I fear 
<lb/>we have a book 
<lb/>thief on board whom 
<lb/>when caught we 
<lb/>shall send down 

     

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001928_0003"><!--pb/@n='36r'--></pb>
<lb/>to be sacrificed to 
<lb/>your Justly offended 
<lb/>sense of Justice &amp; 
<lb/>honour. I am 
<lb/>really very sorry 
<lb/>for the mishap 
<lb/>and will be glad 
<lb/>if you lose some 
<lb/>of <bibl>my books</bibl> in 
<lb/>as silly a manner</p>
<lb/><p>We are ready 
<lb/>to start tomorrow 
<lb/>but fear to go 
<lb/>through bush &amp; <choice><sic>brake</sic><corr>break</corr></choice>

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_001928_0004"><!--pb/@n='36v'--></pb>
<lb/>in thin parts dripping 
<lb/>wet a la <persName>Waller</persName>
<lb/>even should the 
<lb/>rain keep away 
<lb/>pains from the 
<lb/>back of one's thighs 
<lb/>With kind words to 
<lb/><persName>Procter</persName> &amp; <persName>Rowley</persName></p>
<lb/><p rend="center">I am &amp;c</p>
<lb/><p rend="right"><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><persName>King</persName> is getting on nicely 
<lb/>nobody else either 
<lb/>sick or skulking</p>
			
